_______________________________________________________________________________
"Increase Density"         
        Similar to Reduce Weight, the psionicist alters the
        structure of a piece of armor to make it denser and
        therefore more resistant to attack.  However, the
        process also adds weight to the armor, and it is
        more mentally taxing than Reduce Weight.
        The bonus is affected, but not determined, by guild level.
 
SP Cost:  100		Guild Level:  11		Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  increase <object>
